1. Moj prijatelj je gej. (*gej*) (My friend is gay.)
2. Njihov brak je bio gay-friendly. (gay-) (Their marriage was gay-friendly.)
3. Ona je izrazila podršku gej zajednici. (*gej*) (She expressed support for the gay community.)
4. Mnogi se bore za prava gej populacije. (*gej*) (Many are fighting for the rights of the gay population.)
5. Volim da idem u gej klubove. (*gej*) (I love going to gay clubs.)
6. Njegovo ponašanje je bilo pomalo gej. (gej-) (His behavior was somewhat gay.)
7. Gej parada je održana u centru grada. (*Gej*) (The gay parade was held in the city center.)
8. Ne volim kada ljudi koriste reč "gej" kao uvredu. (*gej*) (I don't like when people use the word "gay" as an insult.)
9. Oni su se venčali na gej-friendly lokaciji. (gej-) (They got married at a gay-friendly location.)
10. Gej zajednica traži jednakost pred zakonom. (*Gej*) (The gay community is demanding equality under the law.)